memory.summarizer_summary:
Here's a summary of the latest developments between India and France, based on recent search results:

*   **Defense Deals:** India has entered into a 7.5 billion Rafale-M deal with France ([theasialive.com](https://theasialive.com/indias-7-5-billion-rafale-m-deal-with-france-strategic-power-move-or-pricey-stopgap/2025/05/05/)) and signed a deal for 26 Rafale fighter jets ([france24.com](https://www.france24.com/en/live-news/20250428-india-says-signs-deal-with-france-for-26-rafale-fighter-jets)).
*   **Strengthened Ties:** India and France are strengthening their defense ties with air and maritime cooperation ([indiatoday.in](https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/india-france-strengthen-defence-ties-with-air-maritime-cooperation-2679292-2025-02-13)).
*   **Broader Cooperation:** Discussions between India and France include AI, nuclear deals, and startups, following meetings between Modi and Macron ([indiatoday.in](https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/modi-in-france-ai-nuclear-deal-startups-emmanuel-macron-paris-agreement-2678865-2025-02-12)).
*   **Overall Relations:** Recent developments indicate continued focus on strengthening overall India-France relations ([insightsonindia.com](https://www.insightsonindia.com/2025/02/13/india-france-relations/)).
